                </div>
                <div>
                   <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-purple-600 dark:group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">Real-Time Entegrasyon</h3>
                   <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                       Kafka ve CDC teknolojileriyle veriyi oluştuğu anda yakalayan canlı veri boru hatları.
                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5: Orkestrasyon -->
        <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-orange-500/30 dark:hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-orange-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden">
             <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
             <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">settings_ethernet</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                   <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-600 dark:group-hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">Orkestrasyon</h3>
                   <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                       Airflow ile karmaşık veri iş akışlarını otomatize eden, izlenebilir ve güvenilir sistemler.
                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 6: 7/24 Hizmet -->
        <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-red-500/30 dark:hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-red-500/10 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden">
             <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
             <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-red-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-red-500/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">support_agent</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                   <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors">7/24 Hizmet</h3>
                   <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                       Sistemlerinizin kesintisiz çalışması için uzman ekibimizle 7 gün 24 saat izleme ve destek hizmeti sunuyoruz.
                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

